  "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
  "body": "As specified in the title, this does not work. I used the following syntax in the CRD:\r\n\r\n```\r\nspec:\r\n  versionTag: v0.6.1\r\n  monCount: 3\r\n  dataDirHostPath: /var/lib/rook\r\n  storage:\r\n    useAllNodes: true\r\n    useAllDevices: false\r\n    directories:\r\n    - path: \"/data\"\r\n    storeConfig:\r\n      storeType: bluestore\r\n      databaseSizeMB: 1024\r\n      journalSizeMB: 1024\r\n```\r\nBut the created OSDs ignore this property. I have seen this feature documented. I will take care of the implementation of a solution if no one else decides to do so in the following days.",
